data.text: CDC #DiseaseDetectives keep us safe by ensuring international travel safety guidelines are followed during disease outbreaks. Learn about the Epidemic Intelligence Service training and critical work of its disease detectives: https://t.co/gHAqoNl1c5. #CDCEIS22 https://t.co/AfmhCfg7Di
